English: Defeat these monsters to gain a permanent damage bonus against them.
Spanish: Derrota a estos monstruos para obtener un bonus de daño permamente contra ellos.

English: Jump a certain number of times.
Spanish: Salta un cierto número de veces.

English: Play for a certain number of hours to earn rewards.

English: Unlock rewards at 10, 20, 30, and 40 minutes of playtime. Resets daily at midnight.
Spanish: Juega 10, 20, 30 y 40 minutos para ganar recompensas diarias. Se resetea a medianoche.

English: Unlock a reward for each day you log in.
Spanish: Conéctate una determinada cantidad de veces para ganar recompensas.
